background-color: blue;

/* Hex — paling umum */
color: #ff5733;
background: #f0f0f0;

/* RGB */
color: rgb(255, 87, 51);
background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* a = opacity */
```

```html
<div style="background: #3498db; color: white; padding: 20px;">
