## 1. Arsitektur Aplikasi

### Monolith

Semua kode dalam satu aplikasi.

```
myapp/
├── controllers/
├── services/
├── models/
├── middleware/
├── public/
└── server.ts
```

| Pro | Kontra |
|-----|--------|
| Sederhana, deploy 1 file | Scale = scale semua (boros) |
| Testing gampang | Tech stack kaku |
| Latency rendah (in-process) | Codebase makin gede, onboarding susah |

### N-Tier

Lapisan terpisah (presentation, business, data).

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph "3-Tier Architecture"
        A[Client] --> B[Presentation Layer]
        B --> C[Business Logic Layer]
        C --> D[Data Access Layer]
        D --> E[(Database)]
    end
    style A fill:#e1f5fe
    style B fill:#fff3e0
    style C fill:#c8e6c9
    style D fill:#bbdefb
    style E fill:#ffccbc
```

### Microservices

Setiap fitur/fungsi jadi service sendiri.

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Client] --> B[API Gateway]
    B --> C[User Service]
    B --> D[Product Service]
    B --> E[Order Service]
    B --> F[Payment Service]
    C --> G[(User DB)]
    D --> H[(Product DB)]
    E --> I[(Order DB)]
    F --> J[(Payment DB)]
    style B fill:#fff3e0
    style C fill:#e1bee7
    style D fill:#c8e6c9
    style E fill:#bbdefb
    style F fill:#ffccbc
```

| Pro | Kontra |
|-----|--------|
| Scale per service | Kompleksitas tinggi |
| Tech stack bebas | Network latency |
| Isolasi error | Testing integrasi susah |
| Team bisa independent | Butuh DevOps mumpuni |

