|-----------|----------|
| HTML5 | Struktur halaman |
| Tailwind CSS (CDN) | Styling utility |
| Font Awesome / Heroicons | Ikon skills & sosial media |
| Formspree / Netlify Forms | Contact form backend |
| Vercel / Netlify | Hosting & deploy |

