| Software | Versi Umum | Fungsi |
|----------|-----------|--------|
| VS Code | Latest | Code editor utama |
| XAMPP | 8.x | Apache + MySQL + PHP lokal |
| MySQL / MariaDB | 8.x / 10.x | Database server |
